{"word":"Contracts","slug":"contracts","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Contracts</b> Between Abraham and Abimelech, concerning wells of water<br/> - Established<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=21&verse=32'>Gen 21:32</a> <br/> - Violated<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=26&verse=15'>Gen 26:15</a> <br/> Between Laban and Jacob for Laban's daughter<br/> - First contract established<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=29&verse=20'>Gen 29:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=29&verse=30'>Gen 29:30</a> <br/> - First contract violated<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=29&verse=27'>Gen 29:27</a> <br/> - Second contract established<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=30&verse=34'>Gen 30:34</a> <br/> - Second contract violated<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=30&verse=43'>Gen 30:43</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=31&verse=7'>Gen 31:7</a> <br/> Between Laban and Jacob for cattle<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=30&verse=29'>Gen 30:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=30&verse=34'>Gen 30:34</a><br/><a href='S:Fraud'>Fraud</a><br/> Between Solomon and Hiram<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=5&verse=11'>1Ki 5:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=9&verse=11'>1Ki 9:11</a><br/> Dissolved:<br/> - By mutual consent<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=4&verse=18'>Exo 4:18</a> <br/> - By blotting out<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=51&chapter=2&verse=14'>Col 2:14</a> <br/> Modes of ratifying:<br/> - By giving presents<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=21&verse=30'>Gen 21:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=18&verse=4'>1Sa 18:4</a> <br/> - By consummating in the presence of the public at the gate of the city<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=23&verse=18'>Gen 23:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=8&chapter=4&verse=2'>Rth 4:2</a> <br/> - By erecting a heap of stones<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=31&verse=54'>Gen 31:54</a> <br/> - By oaths<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=26&verse=3'>Gen 26:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=26&verse=31'>Gen 26:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=9&verse=15'>Jos 9:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=9&verse=20'>Jos 9:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=16&verse=16'>1Ch 16:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=6&verse=17'>Heb 6:17</a> <br/> - By joining hands<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=6&verse=1'>Pro 6:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=11&verse=21'>Pro 11:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=17&verse=18'>Pro 17:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=22&verse=26'>Pro 22:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=17&verse=18'>Eze 17:18</a> <br/> - With salt<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=18&verse=19'>Num 18:19</a> <br/> - By taking off the shoe<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=8&chapter=4&verse=8'>Rth 4:8</a> <br/> - Written instrument<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=32&verse=15'>Jer 32:15</a><br/><a href='S:Covenant'>Covenant</a>; <a href='S:Vows'>Vows</a> <br/> Scriptures illustrative of the binding force of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=21&verse=6'>Exo 21:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=6&verse=2'>Lev 6:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=6&verse=7'>Lev 6:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=9&verse=9'>Jos 9:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=9&verse=16'>Jos 9:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=9&verse=27'>Jos 9:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=20&verse=16'>Mat 20:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=3&verse=15'>Gal 3:15</a><br/><a href='S:Covenant'>Covenant</a>; <a href='S:Land'>Land</a>"}]}